definitions.definition: An affluent suburban area in the borough of Camden , London , England ( OS grid ref TQ2685 ) .
A parish and community therein, in Queens County , New Brunswick , Canada .
A suburb and municipality in Montreal , Quebec , Canada .
A town in Carroll County , Maryland .
A town in Rockingham County , New Hampshire .
A census-designated place in Pender County , North Carolina .
A village in Saint Andrew parish, Dominica .
A suburb of Ashburton , Canterbury , New Zealand .
